  I am an Assistant Professor in the <a href="http://math.nmsu.edu/">Department of Mathematical Sciences</a> at <a href="http://nmsu.edu/">New Mexico State University</a>.
 <br />
<br />
Previously, I was a Visiting Assistant Professor in the <a href="http://math.ku.edu/">Department of Mathematics</a> at <a href="http://ku.edu/">University of Kansas</a>. 
<br />
<br />
Before joining KU, I was a Ph.D. student at <a href="http://purdue.edu">Purdue University</a> working under the direction of Professor <a href="http://math.purdue.edu/~ulrich">Bernd Ulrich</a>.</p>

